ONS.\r\n                                        \r\n                                    \r\n                                \r\n                            \r\n                                \r\n                        \r\n                            Booking Details\r\n                            \r\n                                \r\n                                    Kids (Qty)2Number of Nights2Bed5Breakfast5Transportation5.00Airfare5.00Island Hopping5.00\r\n                                \r\n                            \r\n                        \r\n                                \r\n                                \r\n                            \r\n                                Payment Details\r\n                                \r\n                                    \r\n                                        \r\n                                            Amount Paid\r\n                                            ₱1,930.00\r\n                                        \r\n                                        \r\n                                            Date Received\r\n                                            May 21, 2025\r\n                                        \r\n                                        \r\n                                            Payment Method\r\n                                            BDO Transfer\r\n                                        \r\n                                        \r\n                                            Reference Number\r\n                                            N/A\r\n                                        \r\n                                          \r\n                        Status\r\n                        Partially Paid\r\n                    \r\n                                        \r\n                                            Invoice #\r\n                                            5\r\n                                        \r\n                                    \r\