st 3 minutes, your feedback would mean the world to us.\r\n            \r\n        \r\n            We genuinely appreciate your time and your business. Thank you for choosing Vantrippers Travel &amp; Tours!\r\n            Questions or need assistance? We\'re here to help:\r\n            📞 Phone: (+63) 976‑4764187\r\n            ✉️ Email: book@vantripperstravelandtour.com\r\n            🌐 Website: www.vantripperstravelandtours.com\r\n            Best regards,The Vantrippers Travel &amp; Tours Team\r\n            \r\n                © 2025 Vantrippers Travel &amp; Tours. All rights reserved.\r\n            \r\n        \r\n        \n\nBest regards,\nVantrippers Travel & Tours\nvantripperstravelandtoursmain@gmail.com\n0976-476-4187\n\nReply to this email with your feedback!', '2025-05-26 17:37:46', 'sent', '', '', '', 'markguanmontilla@gmail.com', NULL, NULL),
(46, 'CUST_0012', '10', 'Quote for Shan - Vantrippers Travel & Tours', '<!DOCTYPE html>\r\n<html>\r\n<head>\r\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\r\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\r\n    <style>\r\n        body {\r\n            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\r\n            line-height: 1.6;\r\n            color: #333;\r\n            max-width: 600px;\r\n            margin: 0 auto;\r\n            padding: 20px;\r\n            background-color: #f9f9f9;\r\n        }\r\n        .container {\r\n            background-color: #ffffff;\r\n            border-radius: 8px;\r\n            padding: 25px;\r\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\r\n        }\r\n        .logo {\r\n            text-align: center;\r\n            margin-bottom: 25px;\r\n        }\r\n        .logo img {\r\n            max-width: 180px;\r\n            height: auto;\r\n        }\r\n        .quote-info {\r\n            background-color: #f5f5f5;\r\n            border-left: 4px solid #3c8dbc;\r\n            padding: 15px;\r\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\r\n            border-radius: 4px;\r\n        }\r\n        .content {\r\n            margin: 20px 0;\r\n        }\r\n        .signature {\r\n            margin-top: 30px;\r\n            padding-top: 15px;\r\n            border-top: 1px solid #eee;\r\n            font-style: italic;\r\n            color: #555;\r\n        }\r\n        .button {\r\n            display: inline-block;\r\n            background-color: #3c8dbc;\r\n            color: white;\r\n            padding: 10px 20px;\r\n            text-decoration: none;\r\n            border-radius: 4px;\r\n            margin-top: 15px;\r\n        }\r\n        .footer {\r\n            text-align: center;\r\n            margin-top: 30px;\r\n            font-size: 12px;\r\n            color: #777;\r\n        }\r\n    </style>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n    <div class=\"container\">\r\n        <div class=\"logo\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://vantripperstravelandtours.com/images/main_logo.png\" alt=\"Vantrippers Travel & Tours\" />\r\n        </div>\r\n        \r\n        <div class=\"quote-info\">\r\n            <p><strong>Quote Number:</strong> 10</p>\r\n            <p><strong>Date:</strong> May 29, 2025</p>\r\n            <p><strong>Valid Until:</strong> June 1, 2025</p>\r\n        </div>\r\n        \r\n        <div class=\"content\">\r\n                    <div style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6;\">\r\n                    <p style=\"margin: 0 0 0.5em;\">Good Day,</p>\r\n                    <p style=\"margin: 0 0 0.5em;\">\r\n                        Thank you for requesting a quotation for our travel services. Attached to this email, you will find a PDF containing the full details of your personalized package.\r\n                    </p>\r\n                    <p style=\"margin: 0 0 0.5em;\">\r\n                        This quotation is valid for three days from the date of this message. If you would like to confirm your booking, simply reply to this email and we will provide you with payment instructions.\r\n                    </p>\r\n                    <p style=\"margin: 0 0 0.5em;\">\r\n                        If you have any questions, need to make adjustments, or wish to add extra services, please let us know and we will update the quote accordingly.\r\n                    </p>\r\n                    <p style=\"margin: 0 0 0.5em;\">\r\n                        We look forward to helping you create an unforgettable travel experience.\r\n                    </p>\r\n                    <p style=\"margin: 0 0 0.5em;\">\r\n                        Warm regards,<br>\r\n                        Vantrippers Travel &amp; Tours \r\n                    </p>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n        \r\n        <div class=\"signature\">\r\n            <p>Best regards,<br>\r\n            Vantrippers Travel & Tours<br>\r\n            vantripperstravelandtoursmain@