(51, 'CUST_0012', '10', 'Invoice #: 10 - Vantrippers Travel and Tour', '<!DOCTYPE html><html><head><meta charset=\"UTF-8\"></head><body>\r\n                        <p style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">\r\n                        Dear Shan,<br>\r\n\r\n                        <strong>Invoice Amount total: ₱3,800.00</strong><br>\r\n\r\n                        𝗣𝗔𝗬𝗠𝗘𝗡𝗧 𝗧𝗘𝗥𝗠𝗦:\r\n\r\n                        ➤ For guaranteed booking, a reservation/downpayment of 50% is required. \r\n                        The remaining balance should be paid via our bank accounts or GCash one day \r\n                        before the travel dates.\r\n\r\n                        ➤ The reservation/downpayment will be deducted from your total rate. \r\n                                Reservation is non‑refundable but rebookable.\r\n\r\n                        𝗣𝗟𝗘𝗔𝗦𝗘 𝗕𝗘 𝗔𝗗𝗩𝗜𝗦𝗘𝗗:\r\n                        ✹ Additionally, the rates do not include taxes. If you require a service \r\n                        invoice, an additional 3% NONE‑VAT will be applied based on the total amount. \r\n                        However, if you only request a carbonized Acknowledgment Receipt, \r\n                        we can issue it free of charge.\r\n\r\n                        <strong>BDO Savings Account</strong><br>\r\n                        ACCOUNT NAME: VANTRIPPERS TRAVEL AND TOURS<br>\r\n                        ACCOUNT NUMBER: 0086 3013 6885<br><br>\r\n\r\n                        <strong>BPI Savings Account</strong><br>\r\n                        ACCOUNT NAME: VANTRIPPERS TRAVEL AND TOURS<br>\r\n                        ACCOUNT NUMBER: 8369‑7261‑62<br><br>\r\n\r\n                        <strong>GCASH Account</strong><br>\r\n                        ACCOUNT NAME: JANINE GAYAS<br>\r\n                        GCASH NUMBER: 0939 5244 860<br><br>\r\n\r\n                        Questions? 📞0976‑4764187 or click the phone icon above to message us.<br>\r\n                        📧 Or email us at book@vantripperstravelandtour.com\r\n                        </p>\r\n                            </body></html>', '\r\n                        \r\n                        Dear Shan,\r\n\r\n                        Invoice Amount total: ₱3,800.00\r\n\r\n                        𝗣𝗔𝗬𝗠𝗘𝗡𝗧 𝗧𝗘𝗥𝗠𝗦:\r\n\r\n                        ➤ For guaranteed booking, a reservation/downpayment of 50% is required. \r\n                        The remaining balance should be paid via our bank accounts or GCash one day \r\n                        before the travel dates.\r\n\r\n                        ➤ The reservation/downpayment will be deducted from your total rate. \r\n                                Reservation is non‑refundable but rebookable.\r\n\r\n                        𝗣𝗟𝗘𝗔𝗦𝗘 𝗕𝗘 𝗔𝗗𝗩𝗜𝗦𝗘𝗗:\r\n                        ✹ Additionally, the rates do not include taxes. If you require a service \r\n                        invoice, an additional 3% NONE‑VAT will be applied based on the total amount. \r\n                        However, if you only request a carbonized Acknowledgment Receipt, \r\n                        we can issue it free of charge.\r\n\r\n                        BDO Savings Account\r\n                        ACCOUNT NAME: VANTRIPPERS TRAVEL AND TOURS\r\n                        ACCOUNT NUMBER: 0086 3013 6885\r\n\r\n                        BPI Savings Account\r\n                        ACCOUNT NAME: VANTRIPPERS TRAVEL AND TOURS\r\n                        ACCOUNT NUMBER: 8369‑7261‑62\r\n\r\n                        GCASH Account\r\n                        ACCOUNT NAME: JANINE GAYAS\r\n                        GCASH NUMBER: 0939 5244 860\r\n\r\n                        Questions? 📞0976‑4764187 or click the phone icon above to message us.\r\n                        📧 Or email us at book@vantripperstravelandtour.com\r\n                        \r\n                            ', '2025-05-30 05:05:41', 'sent', '', '', 'to', 'edishanleetenorio03@gmail.com', 'invoice_10.pdf', 'C:\\Users\\Edishan Lee\\Ap